targets.rawSql:
SELECT 
    time,
    linear_x AS "Geschwindigkeit (m/s)",
    angular_z AS "Drehrate (rad/s)"
FROM cmd_vel
ORDER BY time DESC
SELECT linear_x FROM cmd_vel ORDER BY time DESC LIMIT 1

SELECT 
    time,
    pose_pose_position_x AS x,
    pose_pose_position_y AS y
FROM odom
ORDER BY time DESC
SELECT linear_x FROM cmd_vel ORDER BY time DESC LIMIT 1

SELECT 
    time,
    percentage * 100 AS "Batterie (%)"
FROM battery_state
ORDER BY time DESC
LIMIT 1

SELECT 
    time,
    voltage AS "Spannung (V)"
FROM battery_state
ORDER BY time DESC
LIMIT 1
SELECT angular_z FROM cmd_vel ORDER BY time DESC LIMIT 1
SELECT data FROM current_screen ORDER BY time DESC LIMIT 1
SELECT data FROM language ORDER BY time DESC LIMIT 1
SELECT time FROM display_start_druecken ORDER BY time DESC LIMIT 1
SELECT time FROM display_stop_druecken ORDER BY time DESC LIMIT 1

targets.queryText: SELECT COUNT(*) AS total FROM sessions
targets.rawQueryText: SELECT COUNT(*) AS total FROM sessions
targets.rawSql: SELECT COUNT("session_id") FROM "sessions";

targets.queryText: SELECT COALESCE(SUM(total_distance_meters), 0) AS total FROM sessions
targets.rawQueryText: SELECT COALESCE(SUM(total_distance_meters), 0) AS total FROM sessions
targets.rawSql: SELECT SUM("total_distance_meters") FROM "sessions";

targets.queryText: SELECT COALESCE(AVG((end_time - start_time) / 1e9), 0) AS avg_duration FROM sessions WHERE end_time IS NOT NULL
targets.rawQueryText: SELECT COALESCE(AVG((end_time - start_time) / 1e9), 0) AS avg_duration FROM sessions WHERE end_time IS NOT NULL
targets.rawSql: SELECT AVG("end_time" - "start_time") FROM "sessions";

targets.queryText: SELECT CASE completion_status WHEN 0 THEN 'PENDING' WHEN 1 THEN 'ACTIVE' WHEN 2 THEN 'PREEMPTED' WHEN 3 THEN 'SUCCEEDED' WHEN 4 THEN 'ABORTED' WHEN 5 THEN 'REJECTED' ELSE 'UNKNOWN' END AS status FROM sessions ORDER BY start_time DESC LIMIT 1
targets.rawQueryText: SELECT CASE completion_status WHEN 0 THEN 'PENDING' WHEN 1 THEN 'ACTIVE' WHEN 2 THEN 'PREEMPTED' WHEN 3 THEN 'SUCCEEDED' WHEN 4 THEN 'ABORTED' WHEN 5 THEN 'REJECTED' ELSE 'UNKNOWN' END AS status FROM sessions ORDER BY start_time DESC LIMIT 1
targets.rawSql: SELECT completion_status from sessions ORDER BY time DESC limit 1;

targets.queryText: SELECT substr(id, 1, 8) AS "ID", datetime(start_time / 1e9, 'unixepoch', 'localtime') AS "Start", round((end_time - start_time) / 1e9, 1) AS "Duration (s)", number_of_messages AS "Msgs", CASE completion_status WHEN 0 THEN 'PENDING' WHEN 1 THEN 'ACTIVE' WHEN 2 THEN 'PREEMPTED' WHEN 3 THEN 'SUCCEEDED' WHEN 4 THEN 'ABORTED' WHEN 5 THEN 'REJECTED' ELSE 'UNKNOWN' END AS "Status", round(total_distance_meters, 2) AS "Dist (m)", round(avg_linear_velocity, 2) AS "Avg Vel" FROM sessions ORDER BY start_time DESC LIMIT 10
targets.rawQueryText: SELECT substr(id, 1, 8) AS "ID", datetime(start_time / 1e9, 'unixepoch', 'localtime') AS "Start", round((end_time - start_time) / 1e9, 1) AS "Duration (s)", number_of_messages AS "Msgs", CASE completion_status WHEN 0 THEN 'PENDING' WHEN 1 THEN 'ACTIVE' WHEN 2 THEN 'PREEMPTED' WHEN 3 THEN 'SUCCEEDED' WHEN 4 THEN 'ABORTED' WHEN 5 THEN 'REJECTED' ELSE 'UNKNOWN' END AS "Status", round(total_distance_meters, 2) AS "Dist (m)", round(avg_linear_velocity, 2) AS "Avg Vel" FROM sessions ORDER BY start_time DESC LIMIT 10
targets.rawSql:
SELECT
  *
From
  sessions
ORDER BY time DESC;
SELECT current_state_name FROM signals_status_update ORDER BY time DESC LIMIT 1
SELECT time, current_state_name FROM signals_status_update ORDER BY time DESC
SELECT COUNT(*) as error_count FROM signals_status_update WHERE current_state IN (4, 5, 6, 7)
SELECT info FROM signals_status_update ORDER BY time DESC LIMIT 1
SELECT time, current_state_name, previous_state_name, info FROM signals_status_update ORDER BY time DESC

SELECT 
    pose_pose_position_x AS "X (m)",
    pose_pose_position_y AS "Y (m)",
    pose_pose_orientation_z AS "Orient. Z",
    pose_pose_orientation_w AS "Orient. W",
    time
FROM odom
ORDER BY time DESC

SELECT 
    percentage AS "Prozent %",
    voltage AS "Volt V",
    time
FROM battery_state
ORDER BY time DESC

SELECT 
    linear_x AS "Linear X (m/s)",
    angular_z AS "Angular Z (rad/s)",
    time
FROM cmd_vel
ORDER BY time DESC

SELECT 
    pose_pose_position_x AS "X (m)",
    pose_pose_position_y AS "Y (m)",
    pose_pose_orientation_z AS "Orient. Z",
    pose_pose_orientation_w AS "Orient. W",
    time
FROM odom
ORDER BY time DESC
